  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "chapterTitle": "序章：从大乱而大治",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "678781_1_509-580",
          "range": "509-580",
          "rangeStart": 509,
          "rangeEnd": 580,
          "markText": "在这个世纪中，有三件大事影响深远，头一件，是北方的六镇之乱，第二件，就是南方的侯景之乱，而在南北两大乱之后发生的第三件大事，却是隋文帝统一中国",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1717549781,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-06-05 09:09:41",
          "chapterUid": 1,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=678781&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=509&rangeEnd=580",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/26b320105a5b7d26be7f4a5?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=509&rangeEnd=580"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "bookReviews": [],
  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "678781_51_381-447",
      "chapterUid": 51,
      "range": "381-447",
      "markText": "民主远非完美的制度，甚至在很多情况下不如专制，但是与专制相比，民主可以在最大程度上避免更多的错误，相对而言，是目前所见的最好的制度。",
      "totalCount": 180,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=678781&chapterUid=51&rangeStart=381&rangeEnd=447",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/26b320105a5b7d26be7f4a5?chapterUid=51&rangeStart=381&rangeEnd=447"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "678781_2_633-703",
      "chapterUid": 2,
      "range": "633-703",
      "markText": "敕勒川， 阴山下， 天似穹庐， 笼盖四野。 天苍苍， 野茫茫， 风吹草低见牛羊。",
      "totalCount": 132,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=678781&chapterUid=2&rangeStart=633&rangeEnd=703",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/26b320105a5b7d26be7f4a5?chapterUid=2&rangeStart=633&rangeEnd=703"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "678781_65_2039-2100",
      "chapterUid": 65,
      "range": "2039-2100",
      "markText": "北齐灭亡对淫荡的胡太后而言简直是一次性解放，她与儿媳妇穆黄花在长安坊间做起了娼妓，成为中国历史上唯一当妓女的皇太后和皇后。",
      "totalCount": 130,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=678781&chapterUid=65&rangeStart=2039&rangeEnd=2100",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/26b320105a5b7d26be7f4a5?chapterUid=65&rangeStart=2039&rangeEnd=2100"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "678781_2_2053-2096",
      "chapterUid": 2,
      "range": "2053-2096",
      "markText": "在这个时候，是绝不可以念小我而废大家的，这是元勰本人性格上的缺陷，也是北魏政权的悲哀。",
      "totalCount": 119,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=678781&chapterUid=2&rangeStart=2053&rangeEnd=2096",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/26b320105a5b7d26be7f4a5?chapterUid=2&rangeStart=2053&rangeEnd=2096"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "678781_27_2789-2887",
      "chapterUid": 27,
      "range": "2789-2887",
      "markText": "一片《敕勒歌》的歌声中，高欢想起了六镇草原上的辽阔天空，想起了怀朔到洛阳的邮差生涯，想起了骑马赶牛的逃难岁月，想起了那个豪气万丈的青年贺六浑。一世坎坷，一路拼搏，今天的你，是憾，是恨，是喜，是哀？",
      "totalCount": 117,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=678781&chapterUid=27&rangeStart=2789&rangeEnd=2887",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/26b320105a5b7d26be7f4a5?chapterUid=27&rangeStart=2789&rangeEnd=2887"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "678781_28_2531-2600",
      "chapterUid": 28,
      "range": "2531-2600",
      "markText": "听过一个笑话：有个和尚劝一个杀牛的改行，说你杀牛杀多了，来世要变牛的。结果杀牛的说：“既然如此，那我还是杀个和尚吧，因为我来世想当和尚。”",
      "totalCount": 105,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=678781&chapterUid=28&rangeStart=2531&rangeEnd=2600",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/26b320105a5b7d26be7f4a5?chapterUid=28&rangeStart=2531&rangeEnd=2600"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "678781_65_1258-1330",
      "chapterUid": 65,
      "range": "1258-1330",
      "markText": "宣政元年（公元578年）五月，周武帝率军兵分五路，北伐突厥。走到半路的云阳（正是宇文泰逝世之地），忽然暴病不起。四天后，武帝驾崩，年仅三十六岁。",
      "totalCount": 105,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=678781&chapterUid=65&rangeStart=1258&rangeEnd=1330",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/26b320105a5b7d26be7f4a5?chapterUid=65&rangeStart=1258&rangeEnd=1330"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "678781_1_581-638",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "581-638",
      "markText": "在大乱之后，中国居然没有像中世纪的罗马四分五裂，反而迎来了大治，以空前强大的大一统形式为这个世纪画上了完美的句号。",
      "totalCount": 104,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=678781&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=581&rangeEnd=638",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/26b320105a5b7d26be7f4a5?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=581&rangeEnd=638"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "678781_15_2720-2793",
      "chapterUid": 15,
      "range": "2720-2793",
      "markText": "说着一声令下，数千名官员上至王公、下至普通大臣，全被军刀砍翻在地。刹那间，黄河边哀嚎漫天，尸首遍野，惨状怖人。这就是著名的河阴惨案，也称河阴之变。",
      "totalCount": 102,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=678781&chapterUid=15&rangeStart=2720&rangeEnd=2793",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/26b320105a5b7d26be7f4a5?chapterUid=15&rangeStart=2720&rangeEnd=2793"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "678781_64_4104-4124",
      "chapterUid": 64,
      "range": "4104-4124",
      "markText": "高欢以一生心血创立的北齐基业，宣告灭亡。",
      "totalCount": 102,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=678781&chapterUid=64&rangeStart=4104&rangeEnd=4124",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/26b320105a5b7d26be7f4a5?chapterUid=64&rangeStart=4104&rangeEnd=4124"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "678781_67_3362-3437",
      "chapterUid": 67,
      "range": "3362-3437",
      "markText": "从西晋八王之乱开始，中华世界二百九十九年的混乱分裂局面结束了。如果愿意，我们还可以上溯到公元184年的黄巾大起义，向四百多年的大分裂时代，做一次告别。",
      "totalCount": 100,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=678781&chapterUid=67&rangeStart=3362&rangeEnd=3437",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/26b320105a5b7d26be7f4a5?chapterUid=67&rangeStart=3362&rangeEnd=3437"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "678781_67_276-306",
      "chapterUid": 67,
      "range": "276-306",
      "markText": "如果能把作诗的本事，用在思考国家时事的安危上，也不至于亡国了",
      "totalCount": 96,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=678781&chapterUid=67&rangeStart=276&rangeEnd=306",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/26b320105a5b7d26be7f4a5?chapterUid=67&rangeStart=276&rangeEnd=306"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "678781_27_2910-2967",
      "chapterUid": 27,
      "range": "2910-2967",
      "markText": "十四年，以早婚早育的北朝人的标准，是一代人的时光。临到末了，我们还是忍不住问一个很俗的问题：高欢与宇文泰，谁更强？",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=678781&chapterUid=27&rangeStart=2910&rangeEnd=2967",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/26b320105a5b7d26be7f4a5?chapterUid=27&rangeStart=2910&rangeEnd=2967"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "678781_2_1660-1692",
      "chapterUid": 2,
      "range": "1660-1692",
      "markText": "北魏皇帝的成熟年龄不断延迟，不知道这是否也与汉化程度的加深有关系",
      "totalCount": 85,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=678781&chapterUid=2&rangeStart=1660&rangeEnd=1692",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/26b320105a5b7d26be7f4a5?chapterUid=2&rangeStart=1660&rangeEnd=1692"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "678781_16_1033-1082",
